            {
              "id": "s1",
              "text_en": "Block B has no idea whether A is above or C is below. It only feels forces acting on its own surface."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2",
              "text_en": "N one is a downward force. N two is an upward force. The weight is downward."
            },
            {
              "id": "s3",
              "text_en": "Write Newton's second law directly: sum of forces in y equals N two minus N one minus mg equals zero."
            },
            {
              "id": "s4",
              "text_en": "The free body diagram turned a complicated system into a single clean equation. That is its real power."
            }
          ]
        },
