              {
                "id": "s2",
                "text_en": "If you draw two bodies together, you would need to show the action-reaction pair of internal forces between them."
              },
              {
                "id": "s3",
                "text_en": "Those internal forces cancel each other, so the diagram tells you nothing useful."
              },
              {
                "id": "s4",
                "text_en": "One FBD means one body. Three stacked blocks means three separate FBDs."
              }
            ]
          },
